<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PeruTM6.2">
<l>keṇṭaiyoṇ kaṇmaṭa vāḷorutti kīḻai yakattut tayirkaṭaiyak</l>
<l>kaṇṭollai nāṉuṅ kaṭaivaṉeṉṟu kaḷḷa viḻiyaiviḻit tuppukku</l>
<l>vaṇṭamar pūṅkuḻal tāḻntulāva vāṇmukam vērppaccev vāytuṭippat</l>
<l>taṇṭayir nīkaṭain tiṭṭavaṇṇan tāmōta rāmey yaṟivaṉāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Seeing an [innocent] woman with barbus[-like] shiny eyes churning curds in the eastern house,</l>
<l>saying ‘I shall churn quickly,’ [You] eyed [her] with [Your] stealthy glance, and slipped in.</l>
<l>As the curling-hair with flowers on which bees sit fell low and moved about,</l>
<l>as the bright face perspired, as the red lips quivered:</l>
<l>the way You churned the cool curds, O Dāmodara, truly I know.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
